The &quot;.backup&quot; mechanism is safe - it&#x27;s directly copying the file with &quot;cp&quot; that doesn&#x27;t work.<p>Here&#x27;s how to use .backup:<p><pre><code>    sqlite3 data.db &quot;.backup &#x27;backup.db&#x27;&quot;
</code></pre>
You can also do this:<p><pre><code>   sqlite3 data.db &#x27;VACUUM INTO &quot;backup.db&quot;;&#x27;
</code></pre>
That&#x27;s slower, but results in a smaller backup file: <a href="https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.sqlite.org&#x2F;lang_vacuum.html" rel="nofollow">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.sqlite.org&#x2F;lang_vacuum.html</a>
